{"tid":2487680,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球王級水平震驚全人類！阿仙奴要簽連格","createTime":"2021-04-13T17:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T11:40:51.000Z","uid":67144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"12f2665ae971710c0bde328d02adb5cc1d4bb80c","tid":2487680,"uid":67144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT2kfv9D4n6miSzkb37DqrtNZ9get4bpPZGWjiDqAS9mv?filename=640MH62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F640MH62.jpg&h=df31f483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年英超「人氣王」連格喺周日(11日)晚英超，又有出色表現，個人梅開二度，協助韋斯咸以3比2擊敗李斯特城，同屬倫敦球隊嘅阿仙奴亦感受到「連球王」嘅氣場，計劃今夏向曼聯收購呢位28歲英格蘭國腳。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》、《倫敦足球》等傳媒都指阿仙奴早於1月已經有興趣借用連格，但因為曼聯唔想喺季中將佢外借畀爭前4位嘅主要對手，最終去咗韋斯咸。<br />\n<br />\n連格為韋斯咸上陣9場，射入8球及3次助攻，令阿仙奴下定決心，今夏用真金白銀收購呢位中場。由於連格將於2022年夏天約滿，紅魔鬼亦唔可以吊高來賣，只要兵工廠出價合理，曼聯應該會出售連格，估計佢身價達3,000萬鎊。"},{"pid":"730404c6afb6d74dc0a25da528d8d53e13d13c71","tid":2487680,"uid":28202,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n